{"tid":676817,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"福布斯公布2018年全球最有價值100大品牌","createTime":"2018-05-24T16:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T16:54:27.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"77f1362d956a8b322728bef09a9a110793bf0739","tid":676817,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:12:13.000Z","msg":"美國財經雜誌《富比士》公布2018年全球最有價值100大品牌，蘋果（Apple）連續第8年蟬聯第1，且品牌價值比去年增加8%至1828億美元（約5.48兆元台幣），比名列第2的Google整整高出38%，更是同業對手三星電子（SAMSUNG）的2.8倍左右，凸顯出蘋果品牌在消費者心目中無可匹敵的地位。<br />\n<br />\n矽谷科技巨頭名列前茅，除了高居第1的iPhone製造商蘋果，Google、微軟（Microsoft）、臉書（facebook）、亞馬遜（<a href=\"http://amazon.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famazon.com&d=uXFdhwHKVZg4YdekkMzJYRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=5c078239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">amazon.com</a>）分別拿下第2到第5名，且品牌價值均呈雙位數增長，反映出科技當道的時代潮流。<br />\n<br />\n今年上榜的100大品牌，品牌價值合計年增10%至2.15兆美元（約64.41兆元台幣）；其中以科技企業最多，佔了20家，其次是金融服務（13家）、汽車（12家）和消費性包裝產品（或稱快速消費品，11家），零售（9家）和精品業者（6家）也不少。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n若按國家劃分，今年榜上有54家美國品牌，比去年少2家，但數量仍冠居全球；接著是德國（12）和法國（7），日本也有7家上榜，以豐田汽車（第9名）名次最高。<br />\n南韓則有2個品牌上榜，分別為第7名的三星電子及第75名的現代汽車（HYUNDAI）；三星不僅名次比去年的第10名進步，品牌價值也年增25%至476億美元（約1.43兆元台幣）。<br />\n中國只有華為（HUAWEI）上榜，位居第79名，品牌價值年增15%至84億美元（約2516.64億元台幣）。<br />\n<br />\n若論品牌價值增幅最大的企業，影音串流平台NETFLIX無疑是大贏家。拿下第55名的NETFLIX品牌價值年增35%至115億美元（約3445.4億元台幣）；其他如PayPal（增幅33%）、亞馬遜（31%）、Google（30%）、臉書（29%）品牌價值躍增幅度也都很驚人。<br />\n<br />\n此外，今年有6家新進榜企業，包括優衣庫（UNIQLO，第96名）和肯德基（KFC，第100名）；同時也有開拓重工（Caterpillar）和COACH等6家企業落榜。（劉利貞／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180524/640_560e68b67d9864a9f125c377a88e5cc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180524%2F640_560e68b67d9864a9f125c377a88e5cc5.jpg&h=cd352d54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在最新品牌價值排行榜中，科技企業仍名列前茅，且美國企業仍佔超過半數。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180524/640_68610a5db8b4ff043036ee346ca9bbae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180524%2F640_68610a5db8b4ff043036ee346ca9bbae.jpg&h=841bfe83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在亞洲品牌中，僅三星電子和豐田汽車擠入前10名<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180524/1360098/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180524%2F1360098%2F&d=uXFdhwHKVZg4YdekkMzJYRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=ff91868f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180524%2F1360098%2F&h=199b6bcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180524/1360098/</a><br />\n<br />\n德國同日本都幾勁"},{"pid":"378d7b561e7f72db6b639dfffcc90b1a48b4f92b","tid":676817,"uid":33875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:18:18.000Z","msg":"個表點解又中又英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6257e1e65e93d8e0f42a144c3be4785c42994409","tid":676817,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:18:21.000Z","msg":"點解無qq同Alibaba<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3792a1be3feab6b6bfc48d30697b3a3361d799c3","tid":676817,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:26:22.000Z","msg":"Tesla 都無？！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c92e08b5440a7f842f33977fa96d252fa234d2","tid":676817,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:40:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85e474ee94545b908d89214b27ac0842b92aac89","tid":676817,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:43:17.000Z","msg":"GE <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac2d39e3b86c3dac36e6bd9d5a198685ab945e1","tid":676817,"uid":27150,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"97c92e08b5440a7f842f33977fa96d252fa234d2","tid":676817,"uid":767